metadata.name: Zero Genesis Pass
metadata.description:
This Genesis NFT gives lifetime access to ZERO, [Probably Nothing's](https://www.probably0.com) mobile management app and unlocks access to our closed beta.

Holders will be able to provide product feedback and vote on feature prioritization in the future.

We will reveal ZERO at the [Metaverse Miami](https://www.metaverse.miami) VIP party on Tuesday, November 29th.

More details to come!
